s</a></th><td class="infobox-data">5 boroughs</td></tr><tr class="mergedtoprow"><th colspan="2" class="infobox-header">Government<div class="ib-settlement-fn"></div></th></tr><tr class="mergedrow"><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">&#160;•&#160;Body</th><td class="infobox-data agent">Łódź City Council</td></tr><tr class="mergedrow"><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">&#160;•&#160;City mayor</th><td class="infobox-data"><a href="/wiki/Hanna_Zdanowska" title="Hanna Zdanowska">Hanna Zdanowska</a> (<a href="/wiki/Civic_Coalition_(Poland)" title="Civic Coalition (Poland)">KO</a>)</td></tr><tr class="mergedrow"><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">&#160;•&#160;<a href="/wiki/Sejm" title="Sejm">Sejm of Poland</a></th><td class="infobox-data"><a href="/wiki/%C5%81%C3%B3d%C5%BA_(parliamentary_constituency)" class="mw-redirect" title="Łódź (parliamentary constituency)">Łódź</a></td></tr><tr class="mergedtoprow"><th colspan="2" class="infobox-header">Area<div class="ib-settlement-fn"></div></th></tr><tr class="mergedrow"><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">&#160;•&#160;City</th><td class="infobox-data">293.25&#160;km<sup>2</sup> (113.22&#160;sq&#160;mi)</td></tr><tr class="mergedrow"><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">&#160;•&#160;Metro<div class="ib-settlement-fn"></div></th><td class="infobox-data">2,496&#160;km<sup>2</sup> (964&#160;sq&#160;mi)</td></tr><tr class="mergedtoprow"><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Highest&#160;elevation<div class="ib-settlement-fn"></div></th><td class="infobox-data">278&#160;m (912&#160;ft)</td></tr><tr class="mergedbottomrow"><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Lowest&#160;elevation<div class="ib-settlement-fn"></div></th><td class="infobox-data">162&#160;m (531&#160;ft)</td></tr><tr class="mergedtoprow"><th colspan="2" class="infobox-header">Population<div class="ib-settlement-fn"><span class="nowrap">&#160;</span>(30 June 2023)</div></th></tr><tr class="mergedrow"><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">&#160;•&#160;City</th