<li id="cite_note-jaskulski-129"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-jaskulski_129-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-jaskulski_129-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFJaskulskiSzmidt2015" class="citation journal cs1">Jaskulski, Marcin; Szmidt, Aleksander (2015). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.degruyter.com/downloadpdf/j/tour.2015.25.issue-2/tour-2015-0003/tour-2015-0003.xml">"The Tourism Attractiveness of Landforms in Łagiewnicki Forest, Łódź"</a>. <i>Tourism</i>. <b>25</b> (2): 27–35. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<span class="id-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1515%2Ftour-2015-0003">10.1515/tour-2015-0003</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/EISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="EISSN (identifier)">eISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/issn/2080-6922">2080-6922</a>. <a href="/wiki/Hdl_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Hdl (identifier)">hdl</a>:<span class="id-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://hdl.handle.net/11089%2F20692">11089/20692</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/issn/0867-5856">0867-5856</a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">28 July</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Tourism&amp;rft.atitle=The+Tourism+Attractiveness+of+Landforms+in+%C5%81agiewnicki+Forest%2C+%C5%81%C3%B3d%C5%BA&amp;rft.volume=25&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=27-35&amp;rft.date=2015